summary: An Ordinance approving the assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1863, for the improvement of Fifteenth Avenue West, in the City of Seattle, from the south margin of West Newton Street to the north margin of West Armour Street, by planking the same, under Ordinance No. 19509, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel and lot of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
